00:00:00.366 --> 00:00:02.800
一场激烈的拳甲格斗
yī cháng jī liè de quán jiǎ gé dòu
An intense armored fist combat

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.900
看得我和老弟浑身热血沸腾
kàn dé wǒ hé lǎo dì hún shēn rè xuè fèi téng
It got my brother and me extremely fired up

00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:10.900
忍不住也各自制作了一套武器和盔甲
rěn bú zhù yě gè zì zhì zuò le yī tào wǔ qì hé kuī jiǎ
We couldn’t help but each make our own weapons and armor

00:00:11.266 --> 00:00:14.400
准备来一场冷兵器大PK
zhǔn bèi lái yī cháng lěng bīng qì dà PK
Preparing for a cold-weapon showdown

00:01:16.100 --> 00:01:17.366
你认不认输
nǐ rèn bù rèn shū
Do you admit defeat?

00:01:17.666 --> 00:01:18.266
不认
bù rèn
No

00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:20.000
等我升级一下装备
děng wǒ shēng jí yī xià zhuāng bèi
Let me upgrade my equipment

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.566
咱们改日再约一场
zán men gǎi rì zài yuē yī cháng
We’ll schedule another battle another day

00:01:22.366 --> 00:01:22.966
行！
xíng
Alright!

00:01:23.166 --> 00:01:24.266
随时奉陪！
suí shí fèng péi
Anytime!

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:31.433
战败后我总结了一下
zhàn bài hòu wǒ zǒng jié le yī xià
After losing, I reflected on it

00:01:31.433 --> 00:01:33.800
感觉是武器太小的原因
gǎn jué shì wǔ qì tài xiǎo de yuán yīn
I realized my weapon was simply too small

00:01:34.033 --> 00:01:37.266
老弟那把狼牙大锤实在太厉害了
lǎo dì nà bǎ láng yá dà chuí shí zài tài lì hài le
That spiked war hammer my brother had was insanely powerful

00:01:37.433 --> 00:01:38.500
碰到我的时候
pèng dào wǒ de shí hòu
When it struck me

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:41.066
感觉就像被一辆小车撞了似的
gǎn jué jiù xiàng bèi yī liàng xiǎo chē zhuàng le shì de
It felt like being hit by a small car

00:01:42.500 --> 00:01:43.133
如果
rú guǒ
If

00:01:43.133 --> 00:01:46.466
我打造一把《死神》里一护的斩魄大刀
wǒ dǎ zào yī bǎ sǐ shén lǐ yī hù de zhǎn pò dà dāo
I forged Ichigo’s massive Zanpakuto from Bleach

00:01:46.533 --> 00:01:48.366
应该就能打败老弟了吧
yīng gāi jiù néng dǎ bài lǎo dì le ba
I should be able to defeat my brother, right?

00:01:49.266 --> 00:01:51.433
但是那把大刀应该会很重
dàn shì nà bǎ dà dāo yīng gāi huì hěn zhòng
But that sword would probably be very heavy

00:01:51.833 --> 00:01:53.566
我挥舞不动咋办
wǒ huī wǔ bù dòng zǎ bàn
What if I can’t even swing it?

00:01:55.033 --> 00:01:56.966
正当我思考的时候
zhèng dāng wǒ sī kǎo de shí hòu
Just as I was thinking

00:01:56.966 --> 00:01:59.100
一个朋友开着他的挖掘机
yí gè péng yǒu kāi zhe tā de wā jué jī
A friend drove over in his excavator

00:01:59.100 --> 00:02:01.133
来找我帮忙焊铲斗
lái zhǎo wǒ bāng máng hàn chǎn dòu
Asking me to help weld the bucket

00:02:01.733 --> 00:02:03.700
看着这台机械大怪物
kàn zhe zhè tái jī xiè dà guài wù
Looking at this mechanical monster

00:02:03.700 --> 00:02:04.933
我突然想到
wǒ tū rán xiǎng dào
It suddenly hit me

00:02:04.933 --> 00:02:07.400
这个不就是我新的盔甲吗
zhè ge bù jiù shì wǒ xīn de kuī jiǎ ma
Isn’t this my new armor?

00:02:07.600 --> 00:02:09.000
只要稍加改造
zhǐ yào shāo jiā gǎi zào
With a bit of modification

00:02:09.033 --> 00:02:11.166
用机械臂代替手臂
yòng jī xiè bì dài tì shǒu bì
Using mechanical arms instead of human ones

00:02:11.333 --> 00:02:14.500
那样就能轻松的挥舞起斩魄大刀
nà yàng jiù néng qīng sōng de huī wǔ qǐ zhǎn pò dà dāo
I could easily wield the massive Zanpakuto

00:02:14.633 --> 00:02:18.166
到时候战胜老弟简直是易如反掌
dào shí hòu zhàn shèng lǎo dì jiǎn zhí shì yì rú fǎn zhǎng
Beating my brother would be a piece of cake

00:02:27.100 --> 00:02:28.600
打发完朋友之后
dǎ fā wán péng yǒu zhī hòu
After seeing my friend off

00:02:28.600 --> 00:02:31.600
我就迫不及待的开始了改装制作
wǒ jiù pò bù jí dài de kāi shǐ le gǎi zhuāng zhì zuò
I immediately started the modification process

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:19.500
怎么样
zěn me yàng
So what do you think?

00:08:20.033 --> 00:08:21.366
我的新装备还可以吧
wǒ de xīn zhuāng bèi hái kě yǐ ba
Not bad for my new equipment, right?

00:08:22.233 --> 00:08:23.700
以前看《死神》动漫的时候
yǐ qián kàn sǐ shén dòng màn de shí hòu
When I watched Bleach in the past

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:25.833
就特别喜欢一护的这柄斩魄大刀
jiù tè bié xǐ huān yī hù de zhè bǐng zhǎn pò dà dāo
I especially loved Ichigo’s Zanpakuto

00:08:26.333 --> 00:08:28.100
现在终于做了出来
xiàn zài zhōng yú zuò le chū lái
Now I’ve finally made it

00:08:28.400 --> 00:08:30.133
有了挖掘机的辅助
yǒu le wā jué jī de fǔ zhù
With the help of the excavator

00:08:30.333 --> 00:08:32.700
即使这么大也能轻松挥舞
jí shǐ zhè me dà yě néng qīng sōng huī wǔ
Even something this huge is easy to swing

00:08:32.900 --> 00:08:35.200
我在这个手的背面还安装了一个音响
wǒ zài zhè ge shǒu de bèi miàn hái ān zhuāng le yí gè yīn xiǎng
I also installed a speaker on the back of this arm

00:08:35.900 --> 00:08:37.000
这是它的开关
zhè shì tā de kāi guān
This is its switch

00:08:41.700 --> 00:08:44.000
这样我们在出场或使用它的时候
zhè yàng wǒ men zài chū chǎng huò shǐ yòng tā de shí hòu
So when we make our entrance or use it

00:08:44.133 --> 00:08:46.700
还可以放点压迫感的音乐震慑对方
hái kě yǐ fàng diǎn yā pò gǎn de yīn yuè zhèn shè duì fāng
We can play some intimidating music to pressure our opponent

00:08:46.900 --> 00:08:48.133
像这样
xiàng zhè yàng
Like this

00:08:54.700 --> 00:08:57.500
好了接下来我们就测试一下它的威力如何
hǎo le jiē xià lái wǒ men jiù cè shì yī xià tā de wēi lì rú hé
Alright, next let’s test how powerful it really is

00:08:59.033 --> 00:09:00.266
我们先拿这个大西瓜
wǒ men xiān ná zhè ge dà xī guā
Let’s start with this big watermelon

00:09:00.266 --> 00:09:02.033
测试一下它劈砍的力量
cè shì yī xià tā pī kǎn de lì liàng
And test its cutting power

00:09:11.966 --> 00:09:13.533
月牙天冲！
yuè yá tiān chōng
Moon Fang Cross Blast!

00:09:24.866 --> 00:09:25.500
大家可以看到
dà jiā kě yǐ kàn dào
As you can see

00:09:25.500 --> 00:09:27.500
它劈砍的力量还是挺大的
tā pī kǎn de lì liàng hái shì tǐng dà de
Its cutting force is quite impressive

00:09:27.966 --> 00:09:29.900
西瓜劈的还挺均匀
xī guā pī de hái tǐng jūn yún
The watermelon was sliced very evenly

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:33.166
让我没想到的是把这个桌子还劈烂了
ràng wǒ méi xiǎng dào de shì bǎ zhè ge zhuō zi hái pī làn le
What I didn’t expect was that it even smashed the table

00:09:33.266 --> 00:09:34.500
威力太大了
wēi lì tài dà le
The power is insane

00:09:35.300 --> 00:09:36.066
好了
hǎo le
Alright

00:09:36.066 --> 00:09:38.266
咱们接下来测试一下它横刀的力量
zán men jiē xià lái cè shì yī xià tā héng dāo de lì liàng
Next, let’s test its horizontal slash power

00:09:38.266 --> 00:09:39.100
怎么样
zěn me yàng
Shall we?

00:09:40.500 --> 00:09:42.500
先准备两个大水缸
xiān zhǔn bèi liǎng gè dà shuǐ gāng
First, prepare two large water tanks

00:09:42.666 --> 00:09:45.266
然后往里面注满水试试看
rán hòu wǎng lǐ miàn zhù mǎn shuǐ shì shì kàn
Then fill them with water and give it a try

00:10:10.300 --> 00:10:11.300
爽死了
shuǎng sǐ le
That was thrilling!

00:10:12.433 --> 00:10:14.233
还是大刀用的过瘾
hái shì dà dāo yòng de guò yǐn
Big swords really feel satisfying to use

00:10:14.533 --> 00:10:17.300
接下来咱们测试一下它的穿刺能力
jiē xià lái zán men cè shì yī xià tā de chuān cì néng lì
Next, let’s test its piercing power

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:19.800
咱们看看
zán men kàn kàn
Let’s see

00:10:19.800 --> 00:10:20.966
这报废的小轿车
zhè bào fèi de xiǎo jiào chē
If this scrapped car

00:10:20.966 --> 00:10:23.300
能不能经受住我这大刀的攻击
néng bù néng jīng shòu zhù wǒ zhè dà dāo de gōng jī
Can withstand the attack of my great blade

00:11:11.500 --> 00:11:12.400
测试完毕
cè shì wán bì
Test complete

00:11:12.633 --> 00:11:14.300
效果还是挺满意的
xiào guǒ hái shì tǐng mǎn yì de
The results are quite satisfying

00:11:15.300 --> 00:11:16.833
看看这几个大窟窿
kàn kàn zhè jǐ gè dà kū lóng
Look at these massive holes

00:11:18.366 --> 00:11:19.800
看看还能不能打开
kàn kàn hái néng bù néng dǎ kāi
Let’s see if it can still open

00:11:21.900 --> 00:11:22.700
这里面
zhè lǐ miàn
Inside here

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:25.600
还能打开
hái néng dǎ kāi
It still opens

00:11:26.900 --> 00:11:27.400
不过
bù guò
However

00:11:27.400 --> 00:11:29.366
在正式跟老弟PK之前
zài zhèng shì gēn lǎo dì PK zhī qián
Before officially PK-ing with my brother

00:11:29.366 --> 00:11:31.266
我还需要熟悉一下操作
wǒ hái xū yào shú xī yī xià cāo zuò
I still need to get familiar with the controls

00:11:31.366 --> 00:11:32.466
拿这辆小车
ná zhè liàng xiǎo chē
Let’s use this small car

00:12:03.733 --> 00:12:04.600
演练完毕
yǎn liàn wán bì
Practice complete

00:12:05.066 --> 00:12:06.966
准备跟老弟再次PK
zhǔn bèi gēn lǎo dì zài cì PK
Ready to challenge my brother again

00:12:16.066 --> 00:12:16.933
老哥呢
lǎo gē ne
Where’s big bro?

00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:19.300
我的大锤已经饥渴难耐了
wǒ de dà chuí yǐ jīng jī kě nán nài le
My war hammer is starving for action

00:13:03.733 --> 00:13:04.500
他这个
tā zhè ge
Isn’t this

00:13:04.500 --> 00:13:05.766
是不是属于在作弊
shì bú shì shǔ yú zài zuò bì
Basically cheating?

00:13:06.833 --> 00:13:09.133
你是不是被我的斩魄大刀吓到了
nǐ shì bú shì bèi wǒ de zhǎn pò dà dāo xià dào le
Are you scared by my Zanpakuto?

00:13:09.400 --> 00:13:10.500
机甲也算甲
jī jiǎ yě suàn jiǎ
Mecha armor still counts as armor

00:13:11.166 --> 00:13:12.633
别以为这样我就怕了你
bié yǐ wéi zhè yàng wǒ jiù pà le nǐ
Don’t think this will make me afraid of you

00:13:14.000 --> 00:13:15.466
让你知道知道我的厉害
ràng nǐ zhī dào zhī dào wǒ de lì hài
Let me show you my true power

00:13:32.166 --> 00:13:32.966
哎呦 我去
āi yōu wǒ qù
Oh damn!

00:13:35.233 --> 00:13:36.433
不玩了不玩了
bù wán le bù wán le
I’m done, I’m done!

00:13:36.500 --> 00:13:37.666
我认输我认输
wǒ rèn shū wǒ rèn shū
I surrender, I surrender!
